  "detailed_description": "Battlegrounds2D.IO is a battle royale game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe goal of Battlegrounds2D.IO is to be the last man standing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou start as a player with no gear!<br />\r\nYou have to find weapons, ammo, armor, medical and other items.<br />\r\nKill every other player, except of your teammates 😏.<br />\r\nBe careful of the danger zone! Do not move outside of the red circle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGear up, loot, kill and get the 🐔 dinner!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis version is the same as the browser version of Battlegrounds2D.IO but completely ad-free.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave fun",
  "about_the_game": "Battlegrounds2D.IO is a battle royale game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe goal of Battlegrounds2D.IO is to be the last man standing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou start as a player with no gear!<br />\r\nYou have to find weapons, ammo, armor, medical and other items.<br />\r\nKill every other player, except of your teammates 😏.<br />\r\nBe careful of the danger zone! Do not move outside of the red circle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGear up, loot, kill and get the 🐔 dinner!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis version is the same as the browser version of Battlegrounds2D.IO but completely ad-free.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave fun",
